Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然 我做得不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日~快乐 生日~快乐 生日~快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这古怪至极怪声是怎么回事啊
